edu.columbia.cs.sdarts.common
Class ModifierNames

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--edu.columbia.cs.sdarts.common.ModifierNames
public class ModifierNames
extends java.lang.Object

A "constants container" for all legal STARTS modifier names and codes. Whenever referring to STARTS modifiers by name or code, always use these constants. This minimizes the impact of change, should a modifier name ever change.
